EN:
Today I brought 2 children to the store, and I felt like I was taken care of.During the meal, the boss noticed that the child couldn't sit still, and took the initiative to take the story book. Because the child didn't eat much, I only ordered a pasta, and I was increased by intimate note (no wonder I feel that it is super full. ) What is even more touching is that the boss noticed that I was going to take medicine, and took a glass of water for me.The good shop found because I came to Wenshan's Parent -Children's Museum, which made me want to leave this comment.

Meal part:
Pink pork chop Italian noodles red sauce is very strong, pork chops are soft and tender, children can eat themselves;
Tomato vegetable soup two picky children to snatch the light, it should also taste good. I only see a lot of ingredients, but I can see that I can’t drink it;
Sweet potato bars are fried very well. There are bags of sweet potatoes in it. It is delicious when eating alone.
Watermelon milk, drinking is really solid watermelon juice+milk, without additional sugar, this is a bonus for mothers who do n’t want to give children too sweet ☺️.
